---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Adventure Activities in Sri Lanka | The Trails of Ceylon" description="Sri Lanka's best adventure activities — surfing Arugam Bay, hiking Adam's Peak, white-water rafting at Kitulgala, cycling the Cultural Triangle, and more." type="article" publishDate="2025-03-15">
  <div class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[350px] overflow-hidden">
    <img src="/images/ella.jpg" alt="Hiking tea estates near Ella, Sri Lanka" class="w-full h-full object-cover" style="object-fit:cover;" fetchpriority="high" width="800" height="600" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/70 text-xs mb-3" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a><span>/</span><a href="/things-to-do" class="hover:text-white">Things to Do</a><span>/</span><span class="text-white">Adventure</span>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="font-serif font-black text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl">Adventure</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 mt-2 text-lg">Surf, hike, raft and cycle Sri Lanka</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-14">
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl">From world-class surf at Arugam Bay to the sacred overnight climb of Adam's Peak, from white-water rafting on the Kelani River to multi-day treks through the Knuckles Range — Sri Lanka punches far above its weight for adventure travel.</p>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {[
        {href:'/things-to-do/surfing',img:'/images/mirissa-beach.jpg',alt:'Surfing Arugam Bay Sri Lanka',badge:'Water',title:'Surfing',desc:'Arugam Bay is Asia\'s most celebrated right-hander. Weligama is perfect for beginners. Two surf seasons mean waves year-round.'},
        {href:'/things-to-do/hiking',img:'/images/ella.jpg',alt:'Hiking Sri Lanka tea estates',badge:'Trekking',title:'Hiking',desc:'Adam\'s Peak overnight pilgrim climb, Ella Rock at dawn, the Horton Plains plateau, multi-day Knuckles treks.'},
        {href:'/things-to-do/white-water-rafting',img:'/images/hero.jpg',alt:'White water rafting Kitulgala Sri Lanka',badge:'Water',title:'White-Water Rafting',desc:'The Kelani River at Kitulgala offers Grade 2–4 rapids through lush jungle — perfect for a half-day adventure.'},
        {href:'/things-to-do/cycling',img:'/images/hero.jpg',alt:'Cycling Cultural Triangle Sri Lanka',badge:'Cycling',title:'Cycling',desc:'Cycle between ancient ruins in the Cultural Triangle, through tea estates in the Hill Country, or around Jaffna\'s island causeway.'},
        {href:'/things-to-do/snorkelling',img:'/images/hero.jpg',alt:'Snorkelling Pigeon Island Sri Lanka',badge:'Water',title:'Snorkelling & Diving',desc:'Pigeon Island off Trincomalee has pristine coral reefs. Hikkaduwa and Unawatuna offer accessible reef snorkelling.'},
      ].map(c=>(
        <a href={c.href} class="group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
            <img src={c.img} alt={c.alt} class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" width="400" height="300" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-ceylon-green-700">{c.badge}</span>
            <h2 class="font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 text-xl mt-1 mb-2">{c.title}</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{c.desc}</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
